3.	How to render a HTML template(file):
Step 1 : Create a template folder in your project where the manage .py file available.  Also create an .html file 
Step 2. Go to settings.py file Inside template mention your template 
Step 3 :  Go to views.py file  where their we need to import the render 
3.1 -> From  django.shortcuts import render 
3.2 -> create a function and the function will return the request and the .html file
3.3 ->  Go to url.py and add your url 
3.4 -> Run the program 
